Enum Constant Detail

CHOICE

public static final NodeType CHOICE
This node type describes an alternation node. Alternations are recognized by '|' character in the syntax.

COMMENT

public static final NodeType COMMENT
This node type describes a comment node.

IDENTIFIER

public static final NodeType IDENTIFIER
This node type describes an identifier node.

LOOP

public static final NodeType LOOP
This node type describes an repetition node. Repetitions are recognized by '{' and '}' characters in the syntax.

OPTION

public static final NodeType OPTION
This node type describes an option node. Options are recognized by '[' and ']' characters in the syntax.

RULE

public static final NodeType RULE
This node type describes a rule node.

SEQUENCE

public static final NodeType SEQUENCE
This node type describes a sequence node.

SYNTAX

public static final NodeType SYNTAX
This node type describes a syntax node. This is the root node of the syntax tree.

TERMINAL

public static final NodeType TERMINAL
This node type describes a terminal node.

NULL

public static final NodeType NULL
This node type describes a null node. Null type nodes are used for testing and preventing NPE.
